narration_text: #C C holds round a bowl with maize
#C C picks out maize in bowl
#C C shakes maize in bowl
#C C carries bowl inside house
#C C shakes bowl
#C C stirs maize in bowl with hand
#C C approaches hand water pump in corner of house room
#C C holds #unsure in pump
#C C pumps water in the bowl
#C C shifts bowl to left hand
#C C washes maize in bowl
#C C washes hand with water from the bowl
#C C shifts bowl to right hand
#C C pumps water in bowl
#C C shifts bowl to left hand
#C C pours water from bowl
#C C carries bowl inside house
#C C shifts bowl to right hand
#C C holds maize in bowl on her way
#C C approaches pot on a cooker
#C C scoops maize from bowl to the pot with hand
#C C shakes hand on pot
#C C carries bowl in house
#C C shifts bowl to right hand
#C C pours water in bowl to water pump corner
#C C walks back
#C C stands near wall
#C C walks back
#C C shifts bowl to left hand
#C C wipes bowl with hand on her way
#C C shifts bowl to right hand
#C C holds hand water pump in room
#C C pumps water in the bowl
#C C carries water
#C C holds bowl down on floor near cooker
#C C carries bowl in room
#C C places bowl on floor
#C C shifts basin with vegetables on floor
#C C walks to seat on the floor
#C C takes potatoes from the seat
#C C carries potatoes
#C C bends
#C C places potatoes down on sack near cooking stand
#C C shifts plates on stand
#C C pushes paper on stand
#C C opens potatoes from paper pack
#C C stands
#C C walks to basin with vegetables in room
#C C takes potato peeler from the basin
#C C walks back to potatoes
#C C wipes peeler on way
#C C bends on potatoes
#C C wipes peeler
#C C picks tray from basin on the stand
#C C places tray on stand nearer her
#C C takes potato
#C C peels potato with the peeler
